@startuml
title Flow A: Instruction Brief Generation

actor User
participant ORCH as "Orchestrator(API)"
participant SNIFF as "Sniffer (Shared)"
participant SYNC as "Synchro"
participant ADPT as "Adapter"
participant INJ as "Injector (Logic)"
participant GEN as "Generator (Task)"
participant LLM as "LLMInterface"

User -> ORCH : "지시사항 만들어줘"(계정 선택됨)
ORCH -> SNIFF : getIndex(region, locale, bucket)
SNIFF --> ORCH : index_ref + trends[]

ORCH -> SYNC : getPersonalContext(persona_account_id)\n(필요 임베딩/히스토리 요약)
SYNC --> ORCH : context_summary (선택)

ORCH -> ADPT : constraints(account_id)
ADPT --> ORCH : {max_len, hash_limit, schedule_support...}

ORCH -> INJ : compose(persona, trends, playbook(account), constraints)
INJ --> ORCH : {brief, metadata, trade_offs}

ORCH -> GEN : buildBriefTask.enqueue(brief, metadata)
GEN -> LLM : ainvoke(brief → 지시사항 JSON)
LLM --> GEN : 지시사항 JSON
GEN --> ORCH : 지시사항 JSON

ORCH --> User : 지시사항 JSON(복사 버튼/딥링크)
@enduml
